Kubernetes

# Deploy to Kubernetes cluster
kubectl apply -f deployment/kubernetes/

# Check deployment status
kubectl get pods -n fraud-detection
kubectl get services -n fraud-detection

AWS SageMaker

# Deploy as SageMaker endpoint
python deployment/sagemaker/deploy.py \
  --model-path s3://your-bucket/models/ \
  --instance-type ml.m5.xlarge \
  --endpoint-name fraud-detection-endpoint


Project Structure

fraud-detect-ml/
├── data/               # Datasets and feature store
├── src/               # Source code
│   ├── data/          # Data loading and processing
│   ├── features/      # Feature engineering
│   ├── models/        # Model training and evaluation
│   ├── serving/       # Model serving API
│   ├── monitoring/    # Monitoring and drift detection
│   └── utils/         # Utility functions
├── tests/             # Test suites
├── notebooks/         # Exploratory analysis
├── deployment/        # Deployment configurations
├── feature_repo/      # Feast feature store definitions
└── models/            # Trained model artifacts
